{"tid":1475353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬事皆備：中國依家就只欠一個大災難","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:47:40.000Z","uid":135762,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3763fb37bbf9750aff9fad18a4c1d851a42c02","tid":1475353,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:38:38.000Z","msg":"其實大陸好多人都覺得香港人訴求係啱<br />\n<br />\n有啲撐共嘅大聲音<br />\n唔洗查根本全部5毛<br />\n喺FB,IG嗰啲根本就只係收錢做嘢<br />\n一日可能要揼萬幾個post/message <br />\n所唔使理佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26q%3D%23京A88519%23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fsearch%3Fcontainerid%3D231522type%253D1%2526q%253D%2523%E4%BA%ACA88519%2523&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=7dcd8281\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26q%3D%23京A88519%23</a><br />\n<br />\n依家大陸班人極反感香港運動<br />\n只不過係人民日報報假新聞<br />\n再加埋五毛煽動 我哋亂打人<br />\n<br />\n只要我哋不斷咁將大量文宣放上微博<br />\n引起關注<br />\n教多啲人翻牆睇真新聞<br />\n<br />\n所以而家最重要嘅係大陸文宣<br />\n<br />\n其實中國已經好多內憂<br />\n貿易戰 內鬥 三峽大壩 人民儲蓄轉股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是但一樣爆<br />\n就一定會封鎖消息<br />\n如果依家做多啲宣傳 <br />\nAC封一個開十個<br />\n俾個預警佢哋<br />\n無論信唔信都好<br />\n已經埋下左伏線<br />\n<br />\n我哋冇錯 只係將真相帶返上去<br />\n放啲佢哋未見過嘅圖片/影片<br />\n可以俾埋啲網台名佢哋follow<br />\n教埋佢哋點樣VPN翻牆<br />\n至於洗唔洗腦<br />\n佢哋可以自己判斷<br />\n佢哋會信有圖有片有目擊者描述<br />\n文字上嘅五毛多啲定係外國嘅網多啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢哋都冇錯 佢哋只係由細俾中共洗腦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用實圖 改變中共地平說</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋要同大陸同胞connect埋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c253c8829a1d042814e665de790ee3cf898180f3","tid":1475353,"uid":56430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"其實香港已經不知不覺將抗爭語言傳到大陸<br />\n而家佢地開口埋口都係廢青、黃屍<br />\n係有d野滲緊入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f36b836dc1473f33cda5a3ca4cdb41dc339926","tid":1475353,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十分同意<br />\n不過要盡快做同集中做<br />\n因為內地可以鎖IP&gt;國內只睇到國內IP既POST"},{"pid":"52722d8924c33297de4da28d5cd0f1b9a7aea0e1","tid":1475353,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"點止哩啲<br />\n舊時毒奶粉果啲都未處理到，啲受難大陸人唔敢出聲炸，仲有近期<br />\n1 武漢事件<br />\n2 樂伽事件<br />\n3 貴州孤兒院性奴<br />\n4 紅黃藍幼稚園性侵<br />\n大把內患，係啲人敢怒不敢言炸"},{"pid":"a5293f1f61b1b9bceb17053f82767ca46660e95a","tid":1475353,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"記住唔係建設民主中國<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係放火燒共產黨後欄<br />\n如果共產黨後欄成功著火,咁我地要既野就一定會有"},{"pid":"99e5cf9e62073cbdde84c2afa199b1d776effd73","tid":1475353,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"Email得唔得"},{"pid":"eb838fe64ced305d522238548681bfad303e79c4","tid":1475353,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYUik2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYUik2W.jpg&h=b7b2e1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hrs0znW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrs0znW.png&h=d1fc316e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqMkznX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-